/*
 * Kim-UUID Comprehensive Test Suite
 *
 * Test Coverage:
 * - UUID v4 generation (random)
 * - UUID v1 generation (time-based)
 * - UUID v3/v5 generation (hash-based, deterministic)
 * - String conversion and parsing
 * - Validation
 * - Comparison and equality
 * - Memory safety
 * - Base64/Base32 encoding
